1. *Bes* je bio poznat po tome što je imao najbolju vinu u okolini. (The *bes* was known for having the best wine in the area.)

2. Ona je uvijek bila *bes*krajna. (She was always *bes*towing.)

3. *Bes*platno je učila strane jezike. (She was learning foreign languages for *free*.)

4. *Bes*konačna večnost je ono što mi daje snagu. (*Infinite* eternity is what gives me strength.)

5. Ona je bila *bes*krajno ljubazna prema nama. (She was *unendingly* kind to us.)

6. *Bes*krajno sam zahvalan na tvojoj pomoći. (I am *endlessly* thankful for your help.)